<h1 style="text-align: center;"><strong>Academic Travel Programs: English Study Abroad<br /></strong></h1>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>Highlights</strong></p>
<p>English Study Abroad is a wonderful opportunity to learn&nbsp;by&nbsp;unusual means in exotic settings.</p>
<ul>
<li>Visit houses, landscapes, and people that inspired artists and authors.</li>
<li>Attend theatre,&nbsp;music and&nbsp;art events, lectures.</li>
<li>Attend Sacrament Meetings in local branches.</li>
<li>Travel by train, ship, coach, bicycle.</li>
<li>Walk gardens, forests,&nbsp;fields, villages, hills.</li>
</ul>
<p>&nbsp;<a href="http://www.byui.edu/english/travel-opportunities/english-study-abroad/application">Application</a> &nbsp; &nbsp; <a href="http://www.byui.edu/english/travel-opportunities/english-study-abroad/classes">Classes</a> &nbsp; &nbsp; <a href="http://www.byui.edu/english/travel-opportunities/english-study-abroad/cost">Cost</a> &nbsp; &nbsp; <a href="http://www.byui.edu/english/travel-opportunities/english-study-abroad/details">Details</a> &nbsp; &nbsp; <a href="http://www.byui.edu/english/travel-opportunities/english-study-abroad/disclaimer">Disclaimer</a> &nbsp; &nbsp; <a href="http://www.byui.edu/english/travel-opportunities/english-study-abroad/packing-details">Packing Details</a> &nbsp; &nbsp; <a href="http://www.byui.edu/english/travel-opportunities/english-study-abroad/places-to-see">Places to See</a> &nbsp; &nbsp; <a href="http://www.byui.edu/english/travel-opportunities/english-study-abroad/photographs">Photographs</a></p>
